The original butterfly brand 🦋 
Find us on Melrose Ave! 👇🏽👇🏽

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Yours Truly Clothing on August 13, 2021 tagging @jayceealcala, and @yourstrulymelrose. May be an image of one or more people and people standing.

node.text: Our YoursTruly flagship. Thank you to everyone who was able to make it out to our new store grand opening on melrose 🦋 We can’t wait to make new memories with all of you and see all the faces that help the brand stand for what we believe in. We owe it all to you 🤍. Our brand is only as strong as our supporters and we are forever thankful to have such a loyal and strong family. Started by us, continued by you 🤍🦋

node.text: Proud to announce the Grand Opening of our Yours Truly Melrose Flagship store this Sunday! 🦋 It has been a rough two years for all of us and we have missed you all so much! We can’t wait to see & meet you all; & build amazing memories with you along this new journey. See you there! 🦋🤍
